  "title": "K01 - Business Analyst",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>The Business Analyst drives product outcomes by delivering actionable insights, conducting market analyses, evaluating solutions, gathering user insights, defining success metrics, building dashboards, and analyzing post-release results. They assess the impact of requested changes and resource requirements to inform decision-making.<br /></p><p><strong>Experience and Skills Needed:</strong><br />Candidates must have a proven record of collecting and synthesizing data to derive actionable insights. Strong communication skills, experience in building dashboards, and the ability to work under pressure are essential. Degrees or diplomas in computer science or product management are a plus</p>",
