    "uen": "199906411R",
    "description": "<h3>WPH Digital, an ISO 9001:2015&nbsp;company, a technology provider focused on innovative digital solutions delivery. Together with our customers in their digital transformation journey, we leverage on the power of digital technology to create new opportunities and achieve improved operational efficiencies.<br>\n</h3>\n<p>At WPH Digital, we employ emerging technologies amd end-to-end digital transformation capabilities, to build innovative apps, platforms, and services that deliver transformative experiences for our customers.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>WPH Digital works with a focused number of clients, this often means you can achieve visible impact with clients far faster than it's possible to achieve in larger organisations. That could involve transforming the way they deliver products to building a brand new app for a fast-growing startup; creating a website for a large household name, or developing a new service platform for businesses.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are seeking dynamic, dedicated, enthusiastic and motivated individuals to partake in our growth. We need strategist, passionate software talents and inspiring technologists to provide your expertise and help us accelerate our digital capabilities.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Be part of a team that shares your passion for all things digital, we are here to support you succeed. If you feel you have what it takes to be part of our dynamic and growing team, please write to us!</p>",
